      "content": "that's a good start. can you go a bit deeper into the 'why' though? like, maybe expand on why he thinks they specifically need British influence. maybe have him mention how the local culture or social structures are essentially holding them back from being 'civilized' compared to the West. just want to make sure the journal really captures that sense of inherent superiority that these officials felt at the time.",
